            "X-Extension-Signature header verification (HMAC-SHA256)",
            "X-Extension-Timestamp replay attack protection (5min window)",
            "X-Machine-ID per-device rate limiting (30 req/min)",
            "EXTENSION_SHARED_SECRET env var on Railway"
